<br>
The best way to raise your defense skill is to accidently gain aggro in an experience group.  Except, as the cleric, this is also the best way to die and get your group killed in the process.  <br>
<br>
Anytime a mob is hitting you, and its an experience mob, your skills have the opportunity to go up.  In my experience, the higher the mob cons to you the more likely a skill increase is. <p><BR>
